{
  "text": "MWM assesses spatial reference memory that relies on extramaze visual cues and the task has been suggested as a preclinical MATRICS rodent task for visual learning and memory [CITATION_1] . Brd1 +/\u00c0 mice did not differ significantly from the WT controls on escape distance (Fig. 1e, Welch's correction, p = 0.229).",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "207364195"
